CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 12, 2013

[Cite as 11/12/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-4943.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-0303. State ex rel. Lacey v. Weaver.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus.

Upon consideration of realtor’s motion for default judgment, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied as moot.
